},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:07:15.000Z","msg":"同意 HA醫護感激大家幫助，但真係唔想用捐贈的物資，因為萬一有咩事HA有藉口會賴貓唔負責任"},{"pid":"6f9444cfec34cb6e580fd0fadf9d8109d2427207","tid":1875534,"uid":210595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"屌 真係唔好再重用<br />\n會contaminated"},{"pid":"03a57793368345048f9443adb98b52d6845de05e","tid":1875534,"uid":141106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:10:10.000Z","msg":"請大家按章工作。。<br />\nReuse完奶左野HA唔會多謝你幫佢慳，反而會話因為你misuse先奶野<br />\n浩園銅像都唔會有份，條命只值12個月糧"},{"pid":"981ad23e46a2be831a995f2ad05059d7fdbf6811","tid":1875534,"uid":299938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:11:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ab73464d898d02cadb497e8f07ae812733029035","tid":1875534,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a09808f3b1c410c76b7e57124579629fbbd63e1d","tid":1875534,"uid":167634,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6fb428e5fb6aa72367019df5e5509f357adb726b","tid":1875534,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"363732504c9befa575cf59dd7903d94a71d7b716","tid":1875534,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:12:16.000Z","msg":"外行教內行，咩世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"真心笑咗，人地食鹽多過你食米，使樓主教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"我要出個標題講我係醫護有幾難？用下個腦先？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"咁即係你係唔係醫護啫?係味講囉.正當性即刻返晒來,唔使俾人覺得外行教內行.你個標題改到咁,講到好似好識嘢咁,真心覺得好on9."},{"pid":"d3e372b44ad30c0f85fa54610d2ae323f23b83fc","tid":1875534,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab73464d898d02